
  1 point = 1 pebble
  
  pebble > 30 days old = 1 bead
  
  bead > 90 days old = 1 button

Credit 

   reg  
     1 point of credibility on registration
   
   dues 
     1 point on paying group dues of any amount
   
Debit
  
  give bead = 3 pebbles
  give button = 3 beads
  hold tiebreaker = 1 button  # only on vote yea into session or vote nay
  take tiebreaker = 3 buttons # available to anyone with 3 buttons, first call
